com.judopay.model

Class TokenRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.judopay.api.Request
      • com.judopay.model.TokenRequest

  • public final class TokenRequest
extends Request
    Represents the data needed to perform a token transaction with the judo API. Use the TokenRequest.Builder for object construction. When creating a TokenRequest the judoId, amount and currency must be provided.
